subs.text:
@cqwww Box breathing is the easiest breathing exercise for me to remember how to do.

Separately: Counting each breath has been the easiest way for me to keep the focus on it. If I get distracted, I just start the count again.

(I have a Headspace subscription as a perk from work.)

